name: Bench Press
description: Lift the barbell from the chest using both arms.

name: Push-Ups
description: Bodyweight exercise focusing on the chest muscles.

name: Dumbbell Flyes
description: Isolation exercise targeting the chest using dumbbells.

name: Pull-Ups
description: Upper-body exercise targeting the back muscles.

name: Bent Over Rows
description: Row a barbell towards the lower chest while bent over.

name: Squats
description: Lower body exercise involving bending the knees and hips.

name: Deadlifts
description: Lift a loaded barbell off the ground using a hip hinge.

name: Lunges
description: Step forward with one leg, lowering the body until both knees are bent.

name: Leg Press
description: Push a weighted platform with the legs in a seated position.

name: Barbell Curls
description: Lift a barbell using the bicep muscles.

name: Dumbbell Hammer Curls
description: Curl dumbbells with a neutral grip, targeting the biceps.

name: Wrist Curls
description: Flex and extend the wrists to target the forearm muscles.

name: Reverse Barbell Curls
description: Curl a barbell with a reverse grip to target the forearms.

name: Dips
description: Dip down between parallel bars, targeting the triceps.

name: Tricep Kickbacks
description: Extend the arm backward using dumbbells to target the triceps.

name: Overhead Press
description: Press a barbell overhead while standing.

name: Lateral Raises
description: Lift dumbbells to the side to target the lateral deltoids.

name: Front Raises
description: Lift dumbbells to the front to target the front deltoids.
